in the period from October 2016 to September 2020 , over- or undercover from the previous calendar period should also be compensated .
the serious increase in charges led Schmidt to the fact that all three waste water plants are relatively small facilities with a very low waste water treatment rate ranging from 6800 to 12000 cubic metres per year .
for example , due to the low distribution base , expenses for necessary repairs of several thousand euros would have a serious impact .
furthermore , wastewater supply in all three plants has been slightly reduced .
