Schmidt pointed out that the mechanical ventilation system had to be replaced in the Azendorf sewage plant due to damage .
in the Welschenkahl pump plant , the nearly 20 @-@ year @-@ old conveyor plants had to be overhauled from scratch , and after almost 20 years of operation the first sewage pond had to be disposed of , sewage sludge disposed of and an additional ventilation facility had to be installed in order to meet water requirements .
