two USB- and HDMI @-@ booths are under the armrest and can therefore be easily reached .
the approximately 29000 euros for the well @-@ equipped top diesel are fine .
those who do not want to invest so much will receive the gasoline from 20000 euros and diesel from 23000 euros .
the engines meet the Euro 6 exhaust standard .
with the HR @-@ V Honda offers a versatile and everyday car .
Airline is not liable : overturning passenger bridge
an airline is not liable for the loss of a passenger on the passenger bridge .
for liability is only possible in the event of risks typical of air traffic , the Oberlandesgericht DÃ¼sseldorf ( Az . : 18 U 124 / 14 ) argued .
the plaintiff had broken a knee gun in the fall .
but the accident could have happened everywhere - it was a general risk to life , according to the Court .
the airline did not have to pay compensation to the man .
disease case : when does the organiser pay
only when the cause of the disease is unquestionably found in the hotel will ill holidaymakers get money back after their journey .
however , this is only the case if more than 10 % of guests have shown the same symptoms .
in the negotiated case , a family was severely ill with diarrhea and burglary on the second day of their Turkish holiday .
she spent almost the entire holiday in the room .
their illness resulted in a defective treatment plant , allegedly polluting marine water .
the family believed that the journey was flawed - and complained against the organizer .
the plaintiff had no success in court .
the treatment plant was indeed defective .
however , the organiser only learned about this shortly before the plaintiff &apos;s departure .
until then , he had to assume that the sea water was in order .
consequently , he did not breach his obligations to provide information ,
since no contamination was found in the samples of water .
the illness of several hotel guests - possibly through infection among themselves - is a general risk to life .
of 691 guests , only 38 were ill .
