Thuringia : Zeiss Meditec approaches sales billion
a high demand for medical technology in Asia has boosted Carl Zeiss Meditec &apos;s sales .
in the first nine months of the fiscal year started in October , Group revenues rose by 6.7 percent to EUR 798.6 million , as announced by the publicly listed company in Jena on Friday .
the Asian business grew disproportionately by 17.1 % .
earnings before interest and taxes rose from EUR 89.5 million to EUR 110.5 million , according to the interim balance sheet .
in this financial year , the Jenaer Medical Technology Group intends to exceed the sales mark of EUR 1 billion , confirmed by the Management Board .
Zeiss Meditec manufactures equipment for medical practices and clinics .
the company , which belongs to the optical and electronic group Carl Zeiss ( Oberkochen ) , employs nearly 3000 people .
